{"tid":296923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將重啓F22戰機生産綫應對中國","createTime":"2017-06-25T04:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T03:02:39.000Z","uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b41335debb6108129e42daa485948e611750a15","tid":296923,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"　　合衆國際社6月25日報導稱，據衆議院軍事委員會發言人说，該委員會目前正在重新審核它去年就重啓F-22&ldquo;猛禽&rdquo;隱形戰鬥機生産綫而下令編撰的一份保密報告。<br />\n<br />\n　　衆議院軍事委員會發言人巴倫&middot;揚史密斯對記者说：&ldquo;我可以證實我們收到了該報告而且正在重新審核它。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　去年4月，該委員會曾問國防部重啓F-22戰鬥機生産綫、生産194架這樣的飛機需要多少資金。<br />\n<br />\n　　目前美國空軍已經擁有187架F-22戰鬥機，若再生産194架，它擁有的F-22&ldquo;猛禽&rdquo;戰鬥機的總數將達到381架。<br />\n<br />\n　　衆議院軍事委員會主席馬克&middot;索恩伯裏和國會其他人認為，當時的國防部長蓋茲2009年關閉F-22戰鬥機生産綫的理由不再適合現在的形勢。<br />\n<br />\n　　索恩伯裏说對付東山再起的俄羅斯和崛起中的中國，必須用不同的、更先進的武器。<br />\n<br />\n　　一些人的估計表明，可能要花費數年、甚至更長時間才能開始交付新的戰鬥機，這一裝備現代化行動需要的資金更是可能達到數百億美元。"},{"pid":"46c8bb2f6155f9077af814853e070cbb86e7a026","tid":296923,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb241532bea337cf1683b40577e0baafd74e000","tid":296923,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:48:46.000Z","msg":"有冇咁撚多資源<br />\n<br />\n又f22 又6 代機"},{"pid":"0c2f3139330518dcecdb0d7159a83d8ff51d4c11","tid":296923,"uid":43,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"廿年前嘅科技都秒中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07be3f10a4f5859b13094255c1ba8e3ae2254d9a","tid":296923,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇咁撚多資源<br />\n<br />\n又f22 又6 代機</blockquote><br />\n開發完F35賣比日本英國之後再開F22<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c072829531a10b123bf6b887ed5b342ee8a770ac","tid":296923,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"3億usd賣比日本有數圍"},{"pid":"6aa25c79fb26e9809bea5ca28a0d98ac27dafed0","tid":296923,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇咁撚多資源<br />\n<br />\n又f22 又6 代機</blockquote><br />\n聽講否決左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣生產完最後批次同後備零件之後<br />\n連模具都銷毀埋<br />\n要重開生產線既成本同生產六代機都差無幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該都係靠存貨同肥電頂到六代機出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fb52f2f6c6484f2bfe20bec1c3ef75d2776f1c","tid":296923,"uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"ab8a617ed1721a3e5b337520c966df6235971e7c","tid":296923,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:10:22.000Z","msg":"點睇"},{"pid":"2628a380f9d9b479087645f15b7f172cafbdce13","tid":296923,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"121"}]}